cmc.controller.search

Class SchoolSearchTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmc.controller.search.SchoolSearchTerm
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleSchoolSearchTerm, IntegerSchoolSearchTerm, StringArraySchoolSearchTerm, StringSchoolSearchTerm

    public abstract class SchoolSearchTerm
extends java.lang.Object
    SchoolSearchTerm is an abstract class modeling a term in a search clause for a single School attribute. Terms can have values and value restrictions. The implememntation for these depends on the type of the extending subclass. The value restrictions are provided through the constructor, and when the value is set, it must pass the value restrictions in order to be accepted.
    Version:
    4/1/16
    Author:
    Alex
